### Health
GET http://localhost:8787/api/health

### Add off-chain royalty
POST http://localhost:8787/api/offchain/royalties
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "marketplace": "OpenSea",
  "nftId": "demo-1",
  "amountUSD": 12.34
}

### List off-chain royalties
GET http://localhost:8787/api/offchain/royalties

### Aggregate (off-chain only in this demo)
GET http://localhost:8787/api/royalties/aggregate

### Create a payout job
POST http://localhost:8787/api/payouts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "USDC",
  "amountUSD": 100,
  "recipients": [
    { "wallet": "0xabc", "percentage": 60 },
    { "wallet": "0xdef", "percentage": 40 }
  ]
}

### List payout jobs
GET http://localhost:8787/api/payouts
